    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE 8IGHT 是一款3D第一人称心理恐怖/故事游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演患有精神分裂症的主角“Max”，在幻觉和幻听的折磨中揭开隐藏的真相，并最终决定他的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重复噩梦的真相、他患上精神分裂症的原因，以及隐藏在其中的一切秘密——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这些心理症状（幻觉和幻听）真的只是精神分裂症造成的吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了打破这噩梦般的命运，主角“Max”在家中行动起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，他必须找到可以缓解症状的药物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许那种药物能解决一切问题……但谁知道呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游玩时间】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一般游玩时间约为<strong>2小时。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 但根据游玩风格、剧情理解和结局数量可能有所不同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【<strong>精神分裂症</strong>】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras/d1e0fb49c658fafeb8e8ee1acf56aa16.avif?t=1743571322\" width=800 height=526 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏主要以患有精神分裂症的主角“Max”的视角展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，游戏中设计了各种增强沉浸感的元素，比如物体突然异常移动、场景突然变化等，来展现主角身为精神分裂症患者的内心状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【<strong>故事</strong>】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras/1081de2e16618ecc8e58fe8fe0e8c208.avif?t=1743571322\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras_big/1081de2e16618ecc8e58fe8fe0e8c208.avif?t=1743571322 width=800 height=486 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏的进行，玩家将逐步揭开主角“Max”的隐藏故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满心理阴暗氛围的世界中，探索“Max”所面临的噩梦般命运的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【<strong>直观的谜题</strong>】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras/72324de5e08ad6ef2e209c7781fa14f1.avif?t=1743571322\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras_big/72324de5e08ad6ef2e209c7781fa14f1.avif?t=1743571322 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了提升游戏体验，同时帮助玩家更好地理解故事，游戏中间穿插了直观的谜题元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据提示解决谜题，推动游戏进展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【<strong>多重结局</strong>】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras/6eb3029cafea8317a71ccf8008fbb7e8.avif?t=1743571322\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316720/extras_big/6eb3029cafea8317a71ccf8008fbb7e8.avif?t=1743571322 width=800 height=478 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在游戏过程中做出的选择会影响结局的不同发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请放心，每个重要选择附近都会有存档点。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>本游戏共有4个结局。(A、B-1、B-2、C)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作主要有3个结局（A、B、C），其中一个结局进一步细分为两个（B-1、B-2）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验多重结局，看看主角“Max”的命运将如何展开。</p>",
